'''Annabel''' is a co-worker of [[Joey Tribbiani|Joey]]'s while he is working as a cologne sampler. She was portrayed by [[Emily Procter]].

She tells Joey of [[The Hombre Man]], who becomes a fellow rival of Joey at work. Annabel initially turns down a date with Joey because The Hombre Man had asked her out first, though later goes out with Joey anyway.
